Package: gpatterns
Title: Single Molecule Methylation Patterns Analysis Suite
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Aviezer", "Lifshitz", email = "aviezer.lifshitz@weizmann.ac.il",
    role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Elad", "Chomsky", role=c("aut")),
    person("Amos", "Tanay", role=c("aut")))
Description: Package for import and analysis of DNA methylation (5mC) data.
    includes basic pipeline to import data from raw fastq, and functions to analyse
    both average methylation and epipolymorphism of multiple samples.
URL: https://tanaylab.bitbucket.io/gpatterns/
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.2),
    misha (>= 3.5.6)
